Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.70,0:04:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法通信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.30,0:04:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換一個頻段試試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.86,0:04:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目標接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.48,0:04:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方向 206-094
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.08,0:04:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離 153,000
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.86,0:04:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對辨認信號無反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.00,0:04:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0120,,對宇宙防禦系統控制室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.96,0:04:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它拒絕了一切通訊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.42,0:04:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼警報沒有響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.77,0:04:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼警報沒有響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.17,0:04:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.06,0:04:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是突然出現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.40,0:04:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是從哪裡來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.73,0:04:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾里克森2 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.69,0:04:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進入攔截路線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.91,0:04:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消失了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.92,0:04:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了　馬上召集全體人員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.65,0:04:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.56,0:04:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.72,0:04:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,防衛系統的事情要等調查完成後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.28,0:05:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在還不能說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.16,0:05:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的　對誰都不能說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.72,0:05:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我思念的故鄉—馬汀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.30,0:05:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是　是不是真的懷有思念之情呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.13,0:05:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到現在為止……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.18,0:05:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的啦 傑特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.09,0:05:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了不能打開的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.86,0:05:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,風會吹進來的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.63,0:05:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜　那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.63,0:05:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.13,0:06:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通過門還有十秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.49,0:06:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您的神色似乎不太好　司令長官殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.28,0:06:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好遠啊  真是好遠的工作啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.33,0:06:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5…4…3…2…1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.00,0:06:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在發出緊急避難命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.10,0:06:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般的市民請遵從工作人員的指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.25,0:06:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前往各指定場所避難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.94,0:06:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.19,0:06:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在發出緊急避難命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.13,0:06:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般的市民請遵從工作人員的指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.18,0:06:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前往各指定場所避難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.13,0:06:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傑特　傑特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.97,0:07:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,侵略軍的艦隊已報上了國名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.66,0:07:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們的名字是「亞維人類帝國」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.72,0:07:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海德星系政府馬上提出締結友好條約談判的邀請
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.20,0:07:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但侵略軍司令長官拒絕了邀請
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.92,0:07:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是回覆說將會進行說明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.85,0:07:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位司令長官的說明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.89,0:07:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會從侵略軍的旗艦上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.20,0:07:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0120,,和亞維人類帝國的事前通信報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.57,0:07:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進行現場轉播
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.16,0:07:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,司令長官既是軍人又是外交官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.48,0:07:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同時也是亞維的皇太子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.89,0:07:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是個怎麼樣的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.49,0:07:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看了可不要吃驚哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.62,0:07:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也用不著那麼緊張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.24,0:07:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,硬要說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.79,0:08:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像是童話中的精靈一樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.86,0:08:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看 出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.62,0:08:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.68,0:08:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就帝國與地上世界的關係進行簡要說明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.54,0:08:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據說他們 是不會變老的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.12,0:08:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論男女都是那麼美麗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.59,0:08:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們說他們也一樣是地球人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.44,0:08:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍微改變了一下遺傳基因而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.57,0:08:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是……稍微……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.56,0:08:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前先說明我的意志就是帝國的意志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.99,0:08:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少在對於貴星系的處理上是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.49,0:08:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先貴星系需要設立貴族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.41,0:08:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在暫時皇帝陛下會成為你們的領主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.12,0:08:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然由於陛下日理萬機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.04,0:08:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們將會向貴星系派出代理官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.94,0:09:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過領主或者代理官通常是不理會瑣碎的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.46,0:09:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.05,0:09:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們認為統治地上世界是一項極不優雅的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.11,0:09:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼口氣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.80,0:09:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說這是威脅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.35,0:09:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據我們的回覆甚至會毫不猶豫地消滅這顆星球？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.21,0:09:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1500個的有人星系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.37,0:09:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20000個以上的半有人星系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.71,0:09:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要和擁有這樣規模支配力的帝國戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.77,0:09:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也只是他們單方面的說法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.44,0:09:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 突然攻過來的敵人的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.35,0:09:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能輕易相信呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.52,0:09:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在地上迎擊的話應該會有些效果吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.85,0:09:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這太愚蠢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.04,0:09:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能不打一仗就認輸呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.81,0:09:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只會不瞭解戰況盲目樂觀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.71,0:09:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請安靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.92,0:09:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要做人身攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.25,0:10:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是有為了這個時候而造的對宇宙防衛系統嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.57,0:10:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不到10架的激光炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.31,0:10:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不足20架的導彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.97,0:10:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.57,0:10:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是國家的名譽問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.42,0:10:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽一下設施部的意見吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.97,0:10:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個 那個嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.91,0:10:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.20,0:10:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海德星系 馬汀政府首席——洛克·凌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.55,0:10:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由於緊急事態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.11,0:10:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這扇門已被封鎖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.78,0:12:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.75,0:12:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.16,0:12:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.08,0:13:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬汀政府向亞維人類帝國投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.74,0:13:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前往愛司扥特公國的客船連卡夫·葛羅梭號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.89,0:13:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將預定在17:30出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.34,0:13:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡 是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.36,0:13:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請還沒有辦理手續的乘客盡快前往第17升降機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.63,0:13:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會這樣是當然的  誰叫我這身打扮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.32,0:13:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.15,0:14:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.78,0:14:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七年前剛來這裡的事已經記不清了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.50,0:14:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之不知道為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.27,0:14:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心裡百感交集
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.75,0:14:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傑特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.14,0:14:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.21,0:14:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來在這裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.93,0:14:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找你很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.05,0:14:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊　對不起　我現在就回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.09,0:14:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  跟我走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.99,0:14:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.49,0:14:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首席官邸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.27,0:14:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到父親那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.53,0:14:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.91,0:14:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別問了　來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.15,0:14:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.39,0:14:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.94,0:14:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有時間了　快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.17,0:15:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生氣了嗎　我道歉嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.96,0:15:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.38,0:15:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個　我們能贏嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.86,0:15:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有輸贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.64,0:15:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒有戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.41,0:15:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼　我們是投降了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.49,0:15:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的　你的父親已決定投降了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.15,0:15:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不　不是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.91,0:15:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們被出賣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.92,0:15:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出……出賣是指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.05,0:15:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洛克那傢伙做了一個交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.49,0:15:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個骯髒的交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.16,0:15:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交易？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.51,0:15:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要像鸚鵡一樣重複我的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.84,0:15:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.51,0:15:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實我也反對戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.67,0:16:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是做出那種交易也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.73,0:16:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畜生　真是看錯洛克了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.78,0:16:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起　這明明不是你的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.28,0:16:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.34,0:16:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全不明白啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.30,0:16:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也不能怪你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.42,0:16:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洛克跟他們做了交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.55,0:16:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我剛剛說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.45,0:16:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,內容即將發表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.64,0:16:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後大家都會知道他背叛了我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.37,0:16:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,背叛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.52,0:16:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而你就是叛徒的兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.60,0:16:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此要到官邸裡避難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.81,0:16:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了不被捉起來毆打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.23,0:16:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會被人打嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.45,0:16:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然的話　家裡還會被投放煙霧彈之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.19,0:16:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼　莉娜怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.08,0:16:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我住在提爾你家裡的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.23,0:16:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有很多人都知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.80,0:16:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經跟她聯絡過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.84,0:17:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.70,0:17:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠照顧自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.07,0:17:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫她先去避難了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.40,0:17:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　她很擔心你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.16,0:17:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和她說了我去找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.79,0:17:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她才安心下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.57,0:17:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.24,0:17:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個　交易是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.67,0:17:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.03,0:17:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在發表之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.39,0:17:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能向一般市民透漏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.61,0:17:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連我也？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.07,0:17:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.23,0:17:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼快就拿出特權階級的腔調了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.14,0:17:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.34,0:17:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快打開全息投影機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.82,0:17:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快要發表了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.79,0:17:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前　亞維軍還沒有任何行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.95,0:17:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凌首席和侵略軍之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.13,0:17:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎正在商談著什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.08,0:17:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據有關人士透露的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.41,0:17:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已確定了要向帝國屈服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.22,0:17:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望這只是空穴來風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.59,0:17:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.24,0:18:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首席官邸預告將於25點整
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.65,0:18:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發表重大聲明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.02,0:18:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有一分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.26,0:18:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是漫長的一分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.40,0:18:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在發表聲明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.15,0:18:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海德星系政府首席洛克·凌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.66,0:18:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於本日23時52分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.84,0:18:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向皇太子兼帝國艦隊司令長官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.49,0:19:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞布里艾爾·尼＝拉姆薩爾·巴爾凱王·杜薩紐殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.37,0:19:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宣佈放棄海德星系的獨立權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.29,0:19:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從今天開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.04,0:19:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們將會成為亞維人類帝國的一部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.76,0:19:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.91,0:19:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接著還有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.37,0:19:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是首席想由海德星系的居民來控制通向其他星系的通道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.61,0:19:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於是提出一項妥協案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.69,0:19:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即是從星界市民當中選出領主的協議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.86,0:19:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事可能嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.83,0:19:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以使宇宙防衛系統無效化的密碼作為代價
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.61,0:19:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的新支配者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.90,0:19:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答應了此事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.79,0:19:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到亞維會害怕防衛系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.67,0:19:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會是一場勢均力敵的戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.42,0:19:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 領主是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.04,0:19:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒到提問時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.71,0:19:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,領主是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.83,0:19:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰啊 領主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.25,0:19:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,領主是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.64,0:19:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.33,0:19:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道會是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.99,0:20:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他人也知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.77,0:20:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此還是想問清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.13,0:20:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快說出我們新主人的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.83,0:20:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變成這樣……不是真的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.01,0:20:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.68,0:20:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕跟大家想的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.86,0:20:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洛克·凌是我們星系的領主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.62,0:20:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 領主就是洛克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.17,0:20:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你的父親所做的卑鄙的交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.73,0:20:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.84,0:20:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然連跟我商量都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.84,0:20:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是覺得這不關秘書官的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.66,0:20:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.00,0:20:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就只有把小孩帶到安全的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.63,0:20:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虧我還當他是親友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.30,0:20:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.25,0:20:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,背叛者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.41,0:20:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼　凌首席
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.05,0:20:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對　凌領主到哪裡去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.74,0:20:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.50,0:20:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了　那傢伙在哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.28,0:20:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個  洛克·凌為了在帝國首都正式受爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.73,0:20:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經登上艦船了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.06,0:20:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃走了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.69,0:20:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才讓發表延遲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.00,0:21:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他會回來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.82,0:21:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.39,0:21:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與包圍著他的帝國護衛兵一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.45,0:21:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.54,0:21:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想回來也肯定回不來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.17,0:21:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帝國會這麼輕易就封他為貴族嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.86,0:21:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙也被騙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.90,0:21:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是諷刺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.01,0:21:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位　請……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.16,0:21:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.40,0:21:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是下一任的領主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.84,0:21:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀 我不應該用這種語氣跟你說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.17,0:21:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你可是我們的王子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.08,0:21:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請原諒我的無禮　殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.36,0:21:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請多寬恕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.29,0:21:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣　提爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.56,0:21:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣說話好不公平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.87,0:21:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.41,0:21:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對你的態度很差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.37,0:21:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.11,0:21:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我無法整理我的情緒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.82,0:21:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畜生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.78,0:21:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經在努力控制不大叫大嚷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.86,0:21:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.84,0:21:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.37,0:22:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.43,0:22:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能問一個問題嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.36,0:22:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.05,0:22:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫莉娜逃走的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.97,0:22:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟她說了交易的事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.19,0:22:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.13,0:22:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為那是對一般市民保密的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.41,0:22:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.50,0:22:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.11,0:22:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我失去了故鄉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.83,0:22:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,故鄉和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.62,0:22:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.57,0:22:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許也失去了親人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.47,0:22:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到這行星上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.91,0:22:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是為了進入學習亞維的事的學校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.72,0:22:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次終於要是去帝都進入軍校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.35,0:22:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.88,0:22:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒有接觸過真正的亞維人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.88,0:22:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實際上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.10,0:23:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天將是第一次
